---
/**
 * ClinicStory - Clinic history and founding story section
 */
---

<section class="clinic-story section" aria-labelledby="story-heading">
  <div class="story-container">
    <div class="story-content">
      <h2 id="story-heading" class="story-title">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="story-lead">
        For over 35 years, Smile Savers has been the trusted dental home for
        families in Woodside and throughout Queens.
      </p>

      <div class="story-text">
        <p>
          Founded in 1987 by Dr. Deepak Bhagat, Smile Savers was built on a
          simple philosophy: every patient deserves exceptional dental care
          delivered with compassion and respect.
        </p>
        <p>
          After graduating from NYU College of Dentistry, Dr. Bhagat saw an
          opportunity to create something different â€” a practice where advanced
          technology meets personalized attention, where patients feel like
          family rather than numbers.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today, that vision continues. Our team has grown, our technology has
          evolved, but our commitment to patient-centered care remains
          unchanged. We've had the privilege of caring for multiple generations
          of families, watching children grow up and bring their own children to
          us.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="story-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">1987</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Founded</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">35+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Years of Service</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">10,000+</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Happy Patients</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="story-image">
      <div class="image-placeholder" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/>
          <polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Smile Savers Clinic</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .clinic-story {
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }

  .story-container {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--spacing-block);
    max-width: var(--container-xl);
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding-inline: var(--spacing-element);
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story-container {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .story-title {
    font-size: var(--font-size-4xl);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .story-lead {
    font-size: var(--font-size-xl);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-text {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: var(--line-height-relaxed);

    p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;

      &:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }
    }
  }

  .story-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-family-heading);
    font-size: var(--font-size-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .story-image {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .image-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 400px;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-light), var(--color-secondary-light));
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);

    span {
      font-weight: var(--font-weight-medium);
    }
  }
</style>
